Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.73,0:00:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.44,0:00:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.42,0:00:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.19,0:00:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.04,0:00:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.15,0:01:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.75,0:01:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.86,0:01:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.23,0:01:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.77,0:01:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯,新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年也請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚要喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.48,0:01:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,回鄉下老家很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,棒個頭啦,在店裡被操得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.85,0:02:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.49,0:02:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有出遠門去玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.43,0:02:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能,我窮死了\N好不容易才湊到回家的車票錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煮好了,煮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天起我要去伊豆一個禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個禮拜有什麼節目嗎?\N比如說約會之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,只有打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\N來啊,喝啊喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不吃這個嗎?\N你想吃其它的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來兩盤黑輪和10串烤雞肉串
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烤雞肉串要鹽味的\N黑輪要多放點芥末喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝啊喝啊,今天我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這樣啊,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#21 五代危機!\N一刻館的小貓物語!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小貓?那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道小貓是什麼嗎?\N就是會小聲喵喵叫的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰在問你這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼時候答應幫你照顧小貓了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.91,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可別說你忘記了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你確實答應過我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽你這麼一提\N難怪你昨晚莫名地拼命灌我酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚的酒錢都是我出的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你的手法太骯髒了,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖喔,乖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙很可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我住的是公寓,不可以養貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍胸脯說“包在我身上”的人是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.26,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊\N你是聽到這傢伙的名字時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛,你怎麼不早說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣,無話可說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.51,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,響子好像也很喜歡你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼要取\N響子這個名字呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.19,0:04:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是管理員的迷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把貓取作管理員的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係,這是我的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我在公寓叫牠的時候怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫響子不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你不叫牠響子的話\N牠不會理你的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.14,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看,13點25分\N開往西伊豆方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好,妳要乖乖的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在外面過夜的話\N至少也請打個電話回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還特地把大門的鎖開著\N等你回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很抱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂動,響…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天天氣真好啊\N(“響”音同“今天”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好險喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被逮到了我可不管妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子餓了嗎?等一下喔\N我馬上弄給妳吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貓罐頭,貓乾糧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.91,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給小貓吃的\N要用溫湯或牛奶將乾糧泡軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啦,我在弄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開罐器在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!居然在這裡尿尿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,響子,給我過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲在那裡也沒有用\N給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快點給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你叫我有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才不是在叫我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.51,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會逃也不會躲的\N到底有什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有叫妳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.24,0:07:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明明有叫啊,你叫“響子”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.65,0:07:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能直接叫妳的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我明明有聽到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你沒事找我囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當…當然沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我走了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來,我不會打妳了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,過來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要隨便叫“響子”這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不行?\N這隻貓叫響子,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.20,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在叫管理員的名字\N聽起來很不愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖喔乖喔,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同學,這是一隻貓耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.78,0:08:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看喔,是母的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看哪裡啊,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這棟公寓可以養貓嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是代為照顧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去向管理員打小報告好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是暫時代為照顧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一頓晚餐,不准討價還價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奢望的也不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一客上等炸蝦飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事後一定要阪本付我這筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,要不要吃啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,請不要隨便給牠東西吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,吃飯囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我看看小貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓管理員發現就沒問題了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貓咪在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然窩在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛喔,還是一隻小貓耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小咪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這隻貓叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫什麼名字嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很舒服是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底叫什麼名字啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就告訴她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是叫妳不要大聲叫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家真的嚇了一跳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,妳在叫我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,妳去應付一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個人不太會說謊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都好,先去應付一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊,快去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,幸好有妳趕來救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,什麼事都沒發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.85,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代突然侵犯我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你這個人怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說謊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美妳這個笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你實在太可恥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣的,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說過了,我不太會說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣,她在說謊,說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要說這種謊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.23,0:12:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄我有這麼好玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦,我不是在捉弄妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是單身嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,竟然都乾不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好命了,都不用煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,阪本那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一切都是妳害的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過了兩三天平安無事的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣漸漸地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像對牠產生了感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也想去上學嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.18,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是誰把小貓帶到教室裡來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我滾回補習班去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.55,0:15:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N你是不是有什麼事情瞞著我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這麼問?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.66,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為惣一郎看到你就一直叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠只是單純地在尋求\N男性之間的友誼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的沒有事情瞞著我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.71,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以進去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,有你的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,誰打來的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾,是個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,是阪本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子?牠很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他居然直呼管理員的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有啊,我每天晚上都抱著牠睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牠都會偷偷地溜到我的棉被裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他們兩人已經在一起了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,找您五十圓,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,一之瀨太太,出來買菜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?一臉笑咪咪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人吃驚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一付純潔乖巧的樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太,到底是什麼事嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.00,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都聽說了喔\N其實不用人家說也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來妳也是個有感情的女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有半夜溜到他棉被裡去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到他自己說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直叫響子響子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,到底跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼時候\N溜到你的棉被裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你每天晚上\N都抱著管理員睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係\N你就老實說出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把事情給我說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.21,0:20:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.88,0:20:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來\N這房間有一股魚腥味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是寵物食物嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.84,0:21:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你吃這種東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貓罐頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,你叫的響子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是貓\N為什麼不一開始就講清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛,真無趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.47,0:22:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.04,0:22:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.11,0:22:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,讓妳幫忙找貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.08,0:22:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.75,0:22:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.02,0:22:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭,怎麼取這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.29,0:22:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.46,0:22:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.80,0:22:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.63,0:22:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.44,0:22:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,來一下,快過來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.71,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,你要我看什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.01,0:23:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.61,0:23:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.72,0:23:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.42,0:23:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裡面到底有什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.85,0:23:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.93,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.77,0:23:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,話說回來\N真不愧是響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.74,0:23:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.61,0:23:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你們怎麼說,我都不會辭掉\N一刻館的管理員工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.52,0:23:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父母怎麼這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.95,0:24:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.69,0:24:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「五代深受打擊!\N響子的辭職宣言」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.82,0:24:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破破爛爛的有什麼關係\N因為這裡是我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.91,0:24:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.86,0:24:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.86,0:24:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.87,0:24:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.01,0:25:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.75,0:25:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕

